Package: artificialLifeR
Type: Package
Title: Educational Simulations for Artificial Life
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Noushin", family = "Nabavi", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "12345678+NoushinN@users.noreply.github.com")
Description: Educational simulations and visualizations for artificial life concepts, including agents, resources, reproduction, mutation, selection, population dynamics, and life-like organization. The package is designed for teaching, conceptual exploration, and science communication rather than empirical biological modeling.
